======================================================================

sunder-bin (A desktop YouTube music client that doesn't spy on you)

Sunder is a lightweight, native desktop music player that streams
music from YouTube without the bloat. Built with Tauri v2 and Rust,
it uses a fraction of the memory that Electron-based alternatives
consume while delivering a buttery smooth UI with hand-crafted
animations.

This is a binary version.

HOME: https://github.com/FrogSnot/Sunder

======================================================================
REQUIRES: webkit2gtk4.1 

